LessonsLearned:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;Recommendations of the investigation committee were as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;a) in the area of exploitation:&lt;br&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- strengthening the communication system to ensure the continuity of data and information exchange;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- equipping the company with devices improving the organization of crisis management;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- extension of cooperation with fire service and emergency service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;b) in the area of investment process:&lt;br&gt;- &lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;at the design stage&lt;/span&gt;, application of additional safety requiremnets &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;concerning rapprochements of gas pipelines to existing infrastructure&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;;&lt;br&gt;- &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;extension of the control of the construction works directly by the investor, with a particular attention to the places of rapprochements of gas pipelines to existing infrastructure&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

EmergencyResponce_Descr:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;1) Evacuation of the people from the dangerous zone;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;2) Protection of buildings exposed to thermal radiation;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;3) Searching for the people and animals in the buildings;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;4)Cutoff the gas supply to the pipeline, reduction fire intensity and extinguising the fire.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

AccidentDescription:
&lt;div class="text-wrap tlid-copy-target"&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;During the building works of the new gas pipeline (ø 700), there was a leak in the high-pressure gas pipeline (already existing nearby, ø 500), resulting in natural gas (methane) leakage followed by a jet fire. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;The probable course of events during the performance of construction works:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- the soil form the trench was stored and gas pipelines in service, in the form of a single pile which significantly exceeded acceptable dimensions and project assumptions;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- dimensions of the soil pile were inconsistent with the design;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;- the excessive load exerted on the 500 mm gas pipeline by the stored soil and much wider and deeper trench resulted in the gas pipeline being pushed outside the trench.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="result-shield-container tlid-copy-target"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

Causes_Description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;Performing the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;construction works against the building permit. &lt;/span&gt;The contractor changed the technology and direction of the pipeline crossing under a road. Sealed chambers were not used.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;The gas pipeline was damaged as a result of external forces - excessive storage of soil for a gas pipeline built in the vicinity.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;The cause of the fire has not been established.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;Irregularities identified were as follows:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;1. &lt;span class="tlid-translation translation"&gt;&lt;span title=""&gt;The performance of hazardous works in the vicinity of functioning gas pipeline was not reported to the Gas Emergency Service.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;2. Change of technology and direction of the crossing under the street.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;3. No tight chambers were used.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;4. Excavated material was stored incorrectly in the form of a single pile.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;5. The pressure caused by the soil stored on the 500 mm gas pipeline pushed the gas pipeline out of the trench.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px"&gt;6. The load resulting the ground pressure and the loss of slope stability created stresses that exceeded the strength of materials, and consequently, led to the pipeline blowout.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
